{"tid":670098,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"爆相爆片：肥叔浸浴　 公園水池變「太子」桑拿","createTime":"2018-05-19T05:18:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-19T06:46:11.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"c91034dc5fd2ca51606facdd846d4f07884a9d23","tid":670098,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T05:18:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180519/20395403\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180519%2F20395403&d=QhqAE%2BowGebsppo1Z3Gpx0jIoeaDRyeQRMy%2FzT52C%2Fo%3D&h=a93ab3aa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180519%2F20395403&h=86db5edc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180519/20395403</a><br />\n<br />\n爆相爆片：肥叔浸浴　<br />\n公園水池變「太子」桑拿<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180519/large/a1503a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180519%2Flarge%2Fa1503a.gif&h=fc457c90&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■阿叔喺公園水池剝光浸浴，自己屋企一樣。<br />\n <br />\n歌仔都有得唱：「我有權散步，你有權洗澡！」呢排日日都超過30℃，熱到小記好想日日浸喺水入面，但太子一位阿叔急不及待，乾脆走落水池降溫，真係熱得咁緊要？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n途人直行直過<br />\n<br />\n讀者Jason喺星期四（17日）凌晨近1點，經過太子始創中心對面嘅公園仔，竟然見到一位光脫脫嘅阿叔，坐咗喺水池入面，Jason話個阿叔年約40、50歲，雖然段片影唔到阿叔正面，但Jason認為係國內同胞，「邊有香港人會咁做」，其實個池周圍都人來人往，但係路人都冇反應，掂行掂過。<br />\n<br />\n從Jason嘅片段見到，阿叔肥屍大隻，一時趴喺度露出肥美嘅屁股，一時又坐番起身，頴吓腳趾非常疏乎。Jason喺現場停留咗10分鐘就走，阿叔都未捨得走，所以都唔清楚阿叔玩咗幾耐。<br />\n<br />\n小記去現場了解，原來公園仔叫「旺角康民角」，水池只有0.2米水深，基本上只係浸過腳眼多啲，街坊話隔籬係直通巴站，平時有好多內地同胞徘徊，入夜後不時有露宿者出沒，但從來未見過有人跳入水池玩。  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n爆相爆片：錫完摑　碌地打　再攬攬　情侶街頭上演　愛情MMA<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n爆相爆片：鬈毛男　機場演脫衣騷"},{"pid":"40033576fb3df1c0738b218f26cf0670713724c4","tid":670098,"uid":140411,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T05:19:11.000Z","msg":"有咩問題？人生好短架，死左就冇架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2438f3742a15004efe1a337be44677872b310992","tid":670098,"uid":182286,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T05:49:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"04cfdba49175f594241dd7a2119a17037e7ab4be","tid":670098,"uid":16676,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T06:04:40.000Z","msg":"太熱訓唔著, 沖下d 汗好訓d <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fozen_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fozen_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e3fe5ab1d7454c2cedfb46ffb962a7f19ab984f","tid":670098,"uid":185683,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T06:06:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1e9d84a81da79bc2ab6a85079e186c7bd319a3ce","tid":670098,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T06:16:30.000Z","msg":"其實唔緊要啲水應該好撚污糟"},{"pid":"1db894468342a2681acc4a0cb18787193ccffda3","tid":670098,"uid":636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T06:18:09.000Z","msg":"其實外國啲人成日都去水池玩水，但唔會除哂衫..."},{"pid":"b5f139f046851341500fc84305993210aaefc54d","tid":670098,"uid":67500,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T06:22:04.000Z","msg":"全身暑假，投奔初夏<br />\n<br />\n00後識條撚"},{"pid":"337d6135eea475a531c7ca1448bd3557d9489c42","tid":670098,"uid":34884,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T06:22:36.000Z","msg":"從Jason嘅片段見到，阿叔肥屍大隻，一時趴喺度露出 <span style=\"color: red;\">肥美嘅屁股</span>，一時又坐番起身，頴吓腳趾非常疏乎。Jason喺現場停留咗10分鐘就走，阿叔都未捨得走，所以都唔清楚阿叔玩咗幾耐。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0005b23e7d398835148d1d244de79232545c40b1","tid":670098,"uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T06:46:11.000Z","msg":